(* prefixSum : int list -> int list
 * REQUIRES: true
 * ENSURES:  prefixSum(L) returns a list whose i-th element is the sum of
 *           the first i elements of L, for i = 1,..., length(L).
 * Examples:
 *  prefixSum nil ==> nil
 *  prefixSum (1::2::3::nil) ==> 1::3::6::nil
 *  prefixSum (5::3::1::nil) ==> 5::8::9::nil
